  "用 @RestController 标注类，并用 @GetMapping(\"/hello\") 暴露一个返回字符串的方法。": "Annotate a class with @RestController and expose a method returning a String via @GetMapping(\"/hello\").",
  "@RestController = @Controller + @ResponseBody，方法的返回值会直接写进 HTTP 响应体，不会被当成视图名。": "@RestController = @Controller + @ResponseBody, so a method's return value is written straight into the HTTP response body instead of being treated as a view name.",
