  "Controller 是请求进系统的第一道门": "The Controller is the first door requests enter through",
  "在 Spring 后端里,浏览器或前端发来的 HTTP 请求,第一个接住它的就是 Controller。Controller 的职责很单一:解析请求、调用业务逻辑、把结果包成响应返回。它不该写复杂的业务计算,那是 Service 的活。这一节先把「门」立起来——一个能响应 GET /hello 的方法。": "In a Spring backend, the first thing that catches an incoming HTTP request from a browser or frontend is the Controller. Its job is narrow: parse the request, call business logic, and wrap the result into a response. It should not contain heavy business computation — that belongs to a Service. This lesson just stands up the door: a method that answers GET /hello.",
  "@RestController 与 @GetMapping": "@RestController and @GetMapping",
  "@RestController 告诉 Spring:这个类里的方法返回值就是响应体本身(通常是 JSON 或纯文本),不要去找 HTML 模板。@GetMapping(\"/hello\") 把方法注册到「GET 方法 + /hello 路径」这条路由上。请求一来,Spring 按路径匹配,找到方法、执行、把返回值写回去。": "@RestController tells Spring that the return value of methods in this class IS the response body (usually JSON or plain text), so don't go looking for an HTML template. @GetMapping(\"/hello\") registers the method on the route 'GET method + /hello path'. When a request arrives, Spring matches by path, finds the method, runs it, and writes the return value back.",
  "最小可用的 REST Controller": "A minimal working REST Controller",
