  "返回 ResponseEntity，找到资源时用 ResponseEntity.ok(...) 返回 200，找不到时用 ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND) 返回 404。": "Return a ResponseEntity: when the resource is found use ResponseEntity.ok(...) for 200, when missing use ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND) for 404.",
  "返回类型要从 String 改成 ResponseEntity<String>,这样你才能同时控制「状态码」和「响应体」。": "Change the return type from String to ResponseEntity<String> so you can control both the status code and the response body together.",
