  "状态码不是装饰品:200 表示成功、404 表示资源不存在,前端和爬虫都靠它判断结果,别一律返回 200。": "Status codes aren't decoration: 200 means success, 404 means the resource is missing; frontends and crawlers rely on them, so don't always return 200.",
