  "返回值不只是「内容」,还有「状态」": "A response is not just 'content', it's also 'status'",
  "前两节里方法直接返回 String,Spring 默认给它配 200 OK。但真实接口经常需要表达「失败」:参数非法该返回 400,资源不存在该返回 404,服务器崩了该返回 500。这些信息装在 HTTP 状态码里,是响应的元数据。要同时掌控状态码和响应体,就别再直接返回裸数据,改用 ResponseEntity 这个「信封」。": "In the last two lessons methods returned a String directly and Spring paired it with 200 OK by default. But real APIs often need to express failure: invalid params should return 400, a missing resource 404, a server crash 500. This information rides in the HTTP status code — metadata of the response. To control both the status code and the body, stop returning raw data and use ResponseEntity, the 'envelope'.",
  "ResponseEntity:把状态码和响应体打包": "ResponseEntity: bundling status code and body",
  "ResponseEntity<T> 是 Spring 提供的响应包装:泛型 T 是响应体的类型,内部还带着状态码和响应头。常用快捷方式:ResponseEntity.ok(body) 直接给 200;ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.XXX).body(...) 自定义任意状态码;只要状态码、没有响应体时用 .build()。HttpStatus 是状态码枚举,NOT_FOUND 就是 404,比手写数字 404 更不容易出错。": "ResponseEntity<T> is Spring's response wrapper: the generic T is the body type, and it also carries the status code and headers. Common shortcuts: ResponseEntity.ok(body) gives 200 directly; ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.XXX).body(...) sets any custom status; use .build() when you want only a status and no body. HttpStatus is the status-code enum, where NOT_FOUND is 404 — safer than hand-typing the number 404.",
  "同一个方法,按结果给出不同状态码": "One method, different status codes by outcome",
  "记住三档常用码:2xx 成功、4xx 客户端错(请求本身有问题)、5xx 服务端错(代码炸了)。404 属于 4xx——是请求方找错了资源,不是服务器的锅。": "Remember three common bands: 2xx success, 4xx client error (the request itself is wrong), 5xx server error (the code blew up). 404 is a 4xx — the caller asked for the wrong resource; it's not the server's fault.",
  "别用「返回 200 + body 里塞 {\"error\":\"not found\"}」来表达失败。这会让所有调用方都以为成功了,缓存、重试、监控全部判断错误。": "Don't express failure as 'return 200 with {\"error\":\"not found\"} in the body'. It makes every caller think it succeeded, breaking caching, retries, and monitoring.",
  "整合:一个会建资源的接口": "Integration: An Endpoint That Creates Resources",
  "整合": "Integrate",
  "写一个 @PostMapping 接口:用 @RequestBody 接住请求体,创建成功时返回 201 Created;并用 @RequestParam 处理列表查询的可选分页参数。": "Write a @PostMapping endpoint that captures the body with @RequestBody and returns 201 Created on success, plus a list endpoint using @RequestParam for an optional paging parameter.",
  "创建资源用 POST,注解是 @PostMapping(\"/tasks\");请求体用 @RequestBody String title 接住。": "Creating a resource uses POST, annotated @PostMapping(\"/tasks\"); capture the body with @RequestBody String title.",
  "201 Created 是「创建成功」的标准码:ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CREATED).body(...)。": "201 Created is the standard code for 'successfully created': ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CREATED).body(...).",
  "可选参数 + 默认值:@RequestParam(defaultValue = \"20\") int limit,请求没带 limit 时就用 20。": "Optional parameter with a default: @RequestParam(defaultValue = \"20\") int limit; when the request omits limit, it uses 20.",
  "用 @PostMapping(\"/tasks\") 映射创建接口": "Map the create endpoint with @PostMapping(\"/tasks\")",
